title: Logiciel Solutions IPO listing today. Check GMP ahead of debut
description: Logiciel Solutions' Rs 40 crore IPO, which opened on November 28 and closed on December 2, is set to debut on the BSE SME platform on December 5. The issue saw selective investor participation, with retail investors driving subscriptions. Grey market activity…
